      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just that professionals don't really get it. they just want to give you more things to \"try\" or more meds to take, but it never actually stops the cycle. it's like a glitch in my life that keeps happening. no matter what i change, the result is always exactly the same. it feels so inevitable.",
